       - Catppuccin Mocha
       - Nord
       - Everforest
       - Solarized
       - Gruvbox
       - Dracula
       - Tokyo-dark/storm/moon
       - Onedark
       - Material
       - Atom One Light
       - Sweet
       - Synthwave 84
       - Atom Dark
       - Oceanic Next
       - Shades of Purple
       - Arc Dark
       - Sunset Aurant
       - Sunset Saffron
       - Sunset Tangerine
       - Cyberpunk
       - Night Owl
       - Github Light (black & white)
       - Srcery (community theme)

       Create your own theme by editing `~/.config/gowall/config.yml`.

